<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>helios::engine::modules::ui::layout::components</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Layout-related<sp/>UI<sp/>components.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>namespace<sp/>contains<sp/>components<sp/>used<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>UI<sp/>layout<sp/>system<sp/>for<sp/>formatting<sp/>and<sp/>presenting<sp/>data<sp/>in<sp/>text<sp/>widgets.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Components</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Component<sp/>|<sp/>Description<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|-----------|-------------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`TimeFormatterComponent`<sp/>|<sp/>Formats<sp/>elapsed<sp/>or<sp/>remaining<sp/>time<sp/>into<sp/>a<sp/>display<sp/>string<sp/>via<sp/>`std::vformat`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`NumberFormatterComponent`<sp/>|<sp/>Formats<sp/>arithmetic<sp/>values<sp/>(scores,<sp/>health,<sp/>etc.)<sp/>into<sp/>a<sp/>display<sp/>string<sp/>via<sp/>`std::vformat`<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>TimeFormatterComponent</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Holds<sp/>a<sp/>format<sp/>string<sp/>and<sp/>a<sp/>`TimeDisplayMode`.<sp/>The<sp/>format<sp/>string<sp/>receives<sp/>two<sp/>integer<sp/>arguments<sp/>(minutes,<sp/>seconds).<sp/>When<sp/>duration<sp/>is<sp/>zero,<sp/>the<sp/>display<sp/>mode<sp/>falls<sp/>back<sp/>to<sp/>`Elapsed`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>NumberFormatterComponent</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Holds<sp/>a<sp/>`std::vformat`-compatible<sp/>format<sp/>string<sp/>that<sp/>accepts<sp/>a<sp/>single<sp/>arithmetic<sp/>argument.<sp/>Used<sp/>by<sp/>binding<sp/>systems<sp/>such<sp/>as<sp/>`Score2UiTextUpdateSystem`<sp/>and<sp/>`MaxScore2UiTextUpdateSystem`<sp/>to<sp/>convert<sp/>numeric<sp/>game<sp/>state<sp/>into<sp/>text.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
